\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Customer Spotlight\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"https://theeventscalendar.com/?p=2431777\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:642:\"<p>Running an independent bookstore these days is not for the faint-hearted. With big retailers selling books online for cheap, maintaining an independent bookstore certainly offers challenges. That’s why it’s essential to have a website to showcase your business, which is precisely what Medina Bookshop does. They not only sell their books in person, but you&#8230;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/blog/customer-examples/featured-calendar-medina-bookshop/\">Featured Calendar: Medina Bookshop</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Jaime\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19843:\"\n<p>Running an independent bookstore these days is not for the faint-hearted. With big retailers selling books online for cheap, maintaining an independent bookstore certainly offers challenges. That’s why it’s essential to have a website to showcase your business, which is precisely what <a href=\"https://medinabookshop.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Medina Bookshop</a> does. They not only sell their books in person, but you can also purchase them online and attend in-store events if you live in the area.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Medina Bookshop, located on the Isle of Wight in England, utilizes the features of our calendaring, ticketing, and filtering plugins to bring their events to the forefront for their community.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ll show you how they make it happen below, so let’s get started!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-the-homepage\">The homepage</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When you first visit the website, you are met with a header that gives you all of the information you need to get started with the bookshop’s website. For some visitors, they’ll want to order books online and for others, they’ll be interested in upcoming events. All of these resources and more can be found in the navigation bar at the top of the homepage.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/tJpb-7H-HiSbzFTgD0dUdZ7q9tvkyk5vl6Yj0bwSppOpEPkiZPAvB7fwbq7CUrWIG02bb96qWgXGxktW8wSbpBewvPUjISU7WqqsWEsvYGQhw6eCJ6NlpynKtH0puKt5QKIIYuyQnGj7beDTOA\" alt=\"Featured calendar homepage\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Scroll down and you’ll see all of their upcoming events at the bookstore, which they’ve conveniently displayed with a customized widget.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"1464\" height=\"1048\" src=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM.png\" alt=\"Forthcoming Events widget\" class=\"wp-image-2431779\" srcset=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM.png 1464w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM-300x215.png 300w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM-665x476.png 665w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM-119x85.png 119w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM-768x550.png 768w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM-430x308.png 430w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM-645x462.png 645w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM-1068x765.png 1068w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM-460x329.png 460w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM-1074x769.png 1074w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM-512x367.png 512w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM-707x506.png 707w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM-600x430.png 600w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.39.26-PM-500x358.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1464px) 100vw, 1464px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Continue further down the homepage to see their recent blog posts, learn about some of their featured authors, and learn more about what books might be available at the shop.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"1584\" height=\"1262\" src=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.41.26-PM.png\" alt=\"Latest news and review for featured calendar\" class=\"wp-image-2431780\" srcset=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.41.26-PM.png 1584w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.41.26-PM-300x239.png 300w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-02-at-12.41.2