6.66%\">\n<p class=\"release-summary__overview has-medium-font-size\">This latest version of Events Calendar Pro features added styling support for <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/native-elementor-widgets-for-events-calendar-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Elementor widgets</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As always, we recommend <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/creating-and-using-a-wordpress-staging-site/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">testing updates</a> on a staging site first, but it should all be smooth sailing.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<h4 id=\"h-new\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.1.0/72x72/2728.png\" alt=\"✨\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> New</h4>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">New features included in this release:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Added Elementor styling support to the Events List widget.</li><li>Added Elementor styling support to the Event Countdown widget.</li><li>Changed action for script enqueues to ensure they are loaded in the correct order on Full Site Editor themes.</li><li>Changed views: <code>v2/widgets/widget-countdown/complete</code></li></ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<h4 id=\"h-fixed\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.1.0/72x72/2705.png\" alt=\"✅\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Fixed</h4>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Bugs that were squashed in this release:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>We now ensure widget filter dropdowns populate correctly in page builders.</li><li>Ensure fast-forward link respects categories from shortcodes.</li><li>Our widgets now play nicely with the Classic Widgets plugin.</li></ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<p></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\"></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\"></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\"></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:33.3%\">\n<h4 id=\"h-translations\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.1.0/72x72/1f5e3.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Translations</h4>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Updated language files and strings:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>41 new strings added</li><li>139 updated</li><li>0 fuzzied</li><li>0 obsoleted</li></ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/release-notes/events-calendar-pro/events-calendar-pro-5-13-1/\">Events Calendar Pro 5.13.1</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"The Events Calendar 5.14.2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1: