t support and solid, reliable service. We confidently recommend them to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</a> users and anyone<a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/guides/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"> starting a new WordPress website</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s begin our list!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"siteground\">1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/siteground/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">SiteGround</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/siteground/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/siteground-homepage-edited.png\" alt=\"SiteGround WordPress Hosting\" class=\"wp-image-87947\" width=\"701\" title=\"SiteGround WordPress Hosting\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/siteground-homepage-edited.png 689w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/siteground-homepage-edited-300x176.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/siteground-homepage-edited-600x353.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/siteground-homepage-edited-102x60.png 102w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/siteground-homepage-edited-153x90.png 153w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 689px) 100vw, 689px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/siteground/\">SiteGround</a> is a popular managed WordPress hosting provider with sky-high ratings in hosting reviews. This is an official WooCommerce- and WordPress-recommended hosting site, adding to its credibility.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>On top of that, SiteGround focuses on making your site super fast and offers advanced<a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wordpress-security/\"> WordPress security solutions</a> to make it virtually hack-proof. They even <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7bFxKceDyJ4\">offer a tutorial</a> on protecting your WordPress site from malware using their web hosting service.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>They also offer location-specific web hosting services with 3 different data centers in the USA, Europe, and Asia. This means you can choose the one closest to you and make your site even faster.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This best web hosting solution grants free WooCommerce access, SSL, daily backups, daily caching, unmetered data transfer, and unlimited email accounts and databases, much of which is done by their in-house WordPress plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to that in-house plugin, it lets you access WordPress Plugins like WPForms and SEO tools like AIOSEO. SiteGround performs automatic WordPress updates, and you can choose to have your automatic updates for plugins alongside the more extensive program.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What’s unique about SiteGround is that it uses Google Cloud Platform, which matches 100% of the energy consumed by its operations with renewable energy.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>SiteGround WordPress Hosting Company: Important Stats</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Speed</strong>: 649 ms</li><li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.98%</li><li><strong>Customer Support</strong>: 5/5</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>SiteGround WordPress Hosting Plans</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>StartUp:</strong> Starts at <strong></strong>$3.99 per month</li><li><strong>GrowBig:</strong> Starts at <strong></strong>$6.99 per month</li><li><strong>GoGeek:</strong> Starts at <strong></strong>$10.69 per month</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-container-627ace1d59fa4 wp-block-buttons\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-theme-background-color has-text-color has-background\" href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/siteground/\" style=\"background-color:#009966\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\">Get started with SiteGround</a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>2. </strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/hostinger/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Hostinger</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/hostinger/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"324\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/hostinger.png\" alt=\"Hostinger best WordPress hosting service pricing\" class=\"wp-image-35526\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/hostinger.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/hostinger-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/hostinger-600x266.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/hostinger/\">Hostinger</a> is becoming more popular day by day. They offer a lot of bang for your buck.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Their web hosting plan includes free email addresses, 100 GB of SSD storage, unlimited bandwidth, a free domain name, and free SSL. They also have 1-click WordPress installation to help you build your site at rocket speed.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With their WordPress optimizer setup, you can rest assured your site is fast. They offer cloud hosting solutions with data centers in the United States, United Kingdom, Netherlands, Lithuania, Singapore, Brazil, and India, resulting in even faster speeds worldwide.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, Hostinger comes with the traditional cPanel dashboard. This control panel focuses on web hosting services and includes all the tools you need to automate and simplify your website hosting experience.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hostinger has a 24/7 live chat support team if you need help. They also offer a 30-day money-back guarantee if required.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Hostinger WordPress Hosting Company: Important Stats</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Speed</strong>: 146 ms</li><li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.9%</li><li><strong>Customer Support</strong>: 5/5</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Hostinger WordPress Hosting Plans</stro