           <h4>First Meet At College</h4><p>We started dating in highschool. I had the hugest crush on him at 21, my stomach would do flips every time I saw him. It all started when he asked me what color my prom dress was so he could match his tie.</p>\n                      <img src=\"http://imagina.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/icon28@2x.png\" width=\"59\" alt=\"First Meet At College\">\n                  <h4>How He Asked?</h4><p>They were with her whole family and he kept trying to get her outside. She just wanted to play with her nephews and didn\'t know what he was up to. Meanwhile her whole family was in on it.</p>\n                      <img src=\"http://imagina.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/icon28@2x.png\" width=\"59\" alt=\"How He Asked?\">\n                  <h4>Will You Marry Me  Cheryl?</h4><p>We went for a weekend vacation. We were together on the beach, and when I saw the ring, I immediately started crying. He looked at me all confused. \'Why are you crying?\' He asked softly will you marry me cheryl?. </p>\n                      <img src=\"http://imagina.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/icon28@2x.png\" width=\"59\" alt=\"Will You Marry Me  Cheryl?\">\n                  <h4>She Hug Him & Said “yes!”</h4><p>We were skiing in Breckenridge. We were at the top of the mountain and he bent down to fix his binding. I was rolling my eyes because I just wanted to get going when all of a sudden he looked up at me with the ring</p>\n                      <img src=\"http://imagina.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/icon28@2x.png\" width=\"59\" alt=\"She Hug Him &amp; Said “yes!”\">\n			<h2>Photography</h2><p>To buy something exceptional, Mindset must be relentlessly focused on the smallest things in wedding related items.</p>\n	  	      <!-- Start -->\n				      <img src=\"http://imagina.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/gallery-image-3.jpg\" alt=\"Celebration\">\n				            <a href=\"http://imagina.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/gallery-image-3.jpg\"></a>\n	