label>TYPE YOUR MESSAGE</label><br />\n   <textarea name=\"your-message\" cols=\"40\" rows=\"10\" aria-invalid=\"false\"></textarea>\n  </p>\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Add Message\" />\n</form>\n			<h2>People Wrote For Us </h2>\n		        <p>We spent a lot of time perfecting the schedule, and making sure everything was perfect, and it really was the perfect day!</p>\n<img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/friend5-65x65.png\" alt=\"\">		        <h4><a href=\"#0\">Helen Henry</a></h4>\n		        <h5>Photographer</h5>\n		        <p>I will always remember my wedding day to be absolutely perfect, and Fidan and Carly were a big part of creating that perfect memory.</p>\n<img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/friend5-65x65.png\" alt=\"\">		        <h4><a href=\"#0\">Rose Barnes</a></h4>\n		        <h5>Creative Head</h5>\n		        <p>Beautiful venue with caring, helpful staff. We were happy to use silver birches for our rehearsal and the cottages, too. The food was delicious, bartenders were fun, and the price seemed too good to be true.</p>\n<img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/friend5-65x65.png\" alt=\"\">		        <h4><a href=\"#0\">Philip Hansen</a></h4>\n		        <h5>Decor Head</h5>\n		        <p>We recently had our Wedding reception at The ceremony Hotel and it was beyond amazing. Our entire family also stayed in the hotel for the weekend and they couldn’t fault the hotel or the staff. Christina, Mick and the whole team were fantastic and everything came together nicely.</p>\n<img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/friend5-65x65.png\" alt=\"\">		        <h4><a href=\"#0\">Charles Sullivan</a></h4>\n		        <h5>Art Director</h5>\n		        <p>Thank you both for your superb work, we are truly amazed by our wedding photos. The photos are absolutely beautiful, you managed to capture our special day moment by moment. Every time we look at the images we are reminded of the emotion, the laughs and fun of the day.</p>\n<img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/friend5-65x65.png\" alt=\"\">		        <h4><a href=\"#0\">Christine Green</a></h4>\n		        <h5>Stage Designer</h5>\n		        <p>A massive Thank you to The ceremony – everyone said it was the best wedding and your staff were all a great bunch of people.</p>\n<img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/friend5-65x65.png\" alt=\"\">		        <h4><a href=\"#0\">Gerald Freeman</a></h4>\n		        <h5>Planner</h5>\n		        <p>We are so very thankful to have had the privilege of working with the perfect planning in our memorable day.</p>\n<img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/friend5-65x65.png\" alt=\"\">		        <h4><a href=\"#0\">Angela Young</a></h4>\n		        <h5>Creative Lead</h5>\n		        <p>You are the main glue that makes everything go well for the wedding day &amp; Our wedding day turned out beautifully.</p>\n<img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/friend5-65x65.png\" alt=\"\">		        <h4><a href=\"#0\">Carl Phillips</a></h4>\n		        <h5>Event Organizer</h5>\n		        <p>There was absolutely no way we were going ahead in the planning of our wedding without theirs professionalism.</p>\n<img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/friend5-65x65.png\" alt=\"\">		        <h4><a href=\"#0\">Robert Jones</a></h4>\n		        <h5>Event Manager</h5>','Guestbook','','publish','closed','closed','','guestbook','','','2019-02-09 09:02:48','2019-02-09 09:02:48','',0,'https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/?page_id=435',0,'page','',0),(442,1,'2019-02-09 09:48:34','2019-02-09 09:48:34','We spent a lot of time perfecting the schedule, and making sure everything was perfect, and it really was the perfect day!','Helen Henry','','p