remony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/icon9@2x.png\" width=\"26\" alt=\"Daniel Taylor\"><h3>Cheryl Spencer</h3><h4>06.10.1994</h4><p>We did meet through a mutual friend at the end of our freshman year in college at Georgia Southern. We got along really well and clicked instantly.</p>              				  					<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"></a>\n				  							  					<a href=\"https://www.twitter.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"></a>\n				  							  					<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"></a>\n          <h2>28.08.2019</h2><h3>Venue at  Lucy Forks, Patriciafur, United States.</h3><a href=\"#0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">RSVP NOW</a>\n			<h2>We Are Getting Married</h2><p>Remaining days for our wedding ceremony, We are expecting all of your presence.</p>\n          <img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/icon19@2x.png\" width=\"30\" alt=\"Remaining days for our Wedding ceremony\">\n          <h3>Remaining days for our Wedding ceremony</h3>\n			<h2>The Wedding Day</h2><p>Our wedding day event order as follows with different cultures and religions will incorporate other elements or swap things around, but if you\'re planning to create a ceremony.</p>\n            <h4>Main Ceremony</h4>\n            <h4>13.08.2019</h4>\n              <h4>Marriage</h4>\n              <h5>09.30am onwards</h5>\n              <img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/icon19@2x.png\" width=\"70\" alt=\"Marriage\"><p>The processional begins with the grandparents, flows through the parents, groom, officiant, wedding party, flower girl, and ring bearer, and ends with the bride making her entrance.</p>\n              <h4>Words of Welcome</h4>\n              <h5>12.30pm onwards</h5>\n              <img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/icon19@2x.png\" width=\"70\" alt=\"Words of Welcome\"><p>Once everyone is in place, the officiant will say a few words of welcome. He or she may thank guests for bearing witness to your union, as well as welcome everyone to your venue and your celebration.</p>\n              <h4>Photography</h4>\n              <h5>2.00pm onwards</h5>\n              <img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/icon19@2x.png\" width=\"70\" alt=\"Photography\"><p>the officiant will offer an introduction and some thoughts on marriage. This could be a brief recounting of your love story, words on what marriage means to you, or a statement about the ceremony to come and represents.</p>\n              <h4>Wedding Cake</h4>\n              <h5>3.30pm onwards</h5>\n              <img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/icon19@2x.png\" width=\"70\" alt=\"Wedding Cake\"><p>A wedding cake is the traditional cake served at wedding receptions following dinner.The wedding cake is served at a wedding breakfast; the \'wedding breakfast\' does not mean the meal will be held in the morning.</p>\n              <h4>Wedding Party</h4>\n              <h5>4.00pm onwards</h5>\n              <img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/icon19@2x.png\" width=\"70\" alt=\"Wedding Party\"><p>At the wedding party the officiant introduces the married couple for the first time. Then, the bride and groom lead the recessional back up the aisle as guests shower you with the rice!</p>\n			<h2>Photography</h2><p>A good snapshot at your wedding can stops a moment from running away.  </p>\n	  	      <!-- Start -->\n				      <img src=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/gallery-image-3.jpg\" alt=\"Celebration\">\n				            <a href=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/gallery-image-3.jpg\"></a>\n				            <h4><a href=\"https://victorthemes.com/themes/ceremony/gallery/c